<br />
<br />Considering that the user registration page already has a custom-added question on it, and won't let you register without answering it correctly, I'd think there has to be a human in the loop somewhere (to at least config their bot for this forum).  So I don't see what else could possibly work, besides changing that question very often or taking the very drastic measures that were just mentioned..  Seems like even a completely coded-from-scratch forum would still get spammed eventually.

		

