		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />By "invite", did you really mean the system where you have to get an invitation code from an existing member out-of-band and then each member can only give out a small number of valid invitation codes per month, like early Orkut? Or do you mean like Advogato, which requires that users be certified by other users in order to post outside their own blog?

		

